    "content": "<p>Technical leader with track record of architecting and deploying enterprise-scale cloud and on-premise applications at AWS. Proven experience building teams from inception through product launch, while mentoring junior engineers to accelerate their growth. Expert in distributed systems design, technical delegation across engineering teams, and security requirements for mission-critical infrastructure.</p>"
