          },
          "description": "<p><strong>On-Prem Device Provisioning Service:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Designed and developed a global hardware provisioning system in AWS. Namely responsible for design of the backend provisioning system API and persistence of inventory. Service is scaled to provision 500k + devices across 100+ Data Centers.</p></li><li><p>Required: Python3, AWS Lambda, AWS DynamoDB, Data Modeling + Access Pattern Analysis</p></li></ul>",
