    "content": "<p>Backend engineer and technical leader with 7+ years building cloud-native services at hyperscale. Track record of launching zero-to-one products as single-threaded owner, from design through production, while leading cross-functional teams and staying close to what customers actually need. Delivered two quarters of estimated engineering effort in a single quarter using AI-assisted development. Experienced in REST API design, distributed systems, DynamoDB data modeling, and collaborating with Product, Design, and Data partners to cut scope to the right MVP and ship fast. Passionate about what AI tooling does to engineering velocity and product quality.</p>"
