          "period": "April 2024 - Present",
          "website": { "url": "", "label": "" },
          "description": "<p><strong>Zero-to-One Internal Service Launch</strong></p><ul><li><p>Designed, built, and launched a new internal AWS service from scratch as single-threaded owner, enabling controls engineers to interact with infrastructure devices via a secure on-demand API. Architected end-to-end: API Gateway (SigV4) → ECS → SSM RunCommand → polling service, with async job completion via S3 event-driven Lambda and Step Functions workflows. Shipped 20+ integration tests and a TypeScript client, unblocking a partner team integration.</p></li><li><p>Delivered two quarters of estimated engineering effort in a single quarter using AI-assisted development. Shipped 58+ code reviews in January 2026 alone with a 1.2 average revision rate, demonstrating a systematic approach to using AI tooling to accelerate delivery without sacrificing quality.</p></li></ul><p><strong>AI-Augmented Engineering and Org Adoption</strong></p><ul><li><p>Built an AI agent that ingests runbooks and accelerates incident triage, processing 170+ tickets and reducing on-call burden across the team. On a severity-2 incident, the agent correlated 4 related tickets and identified root cause within minutes, eliminating a false escalation.</p></li><li><p>Drove AI tooling adoption across 6+ teams: created a shared wiki, ran recurring Lunch and Learns with 15+ attendees, and authored org-wide AI tenets. Featured twice in efficiency reports sent to senior leadership. Four teams now building AI skill packages organically.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Data Instrumentation and Operational Dashboards</strong></p><ul><li><p>Built a reusable CloudWatch dashboard framework using CDK to instrument and monitor distributed systems health across hundreds of sites. Adopted by 10+ engineers across 6+ teams, becoming a critical tool for data-driven operational decision making and leadership reviews.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Leadership and Mentorship</strong></p><ul><li><p>Conducted 10+ interviews annually. Mentored 4+ official mentees across levels and organizations with multiple successful promotions. Served as AppSec Guardian across two organizations totaling 700+ engineers, shepherding 30+ products through security certification and growing the Guardian cohort by 25% through a structured shadow program.</p></li></ul>",
