          "period": "August 2022 - April 2024",
          "website": { "url": "", "label": "" },
          "description": "<p><strong>N-Tier Collaboration Routing Service</strong></p><ul><li><p>Led a team of 13 engineers to architect and deliver a zero-to-one backend REST API enabling secure file exchange between AWS Supply Chain customers and their trading partners. Created high-level system design and delegated 14 low-level design artifacts across 4 engineers. Delivered 14 API endpoints and 35,000 lines of production code across 5 CI/CD pipelines in a 4-month timeline, achieving the General Availability launch bar, AWS's highest deployment standard.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Supply Chain Product Location Service</strong></p><ul><li><p>Architected and delivered a zero-to-one backend REST API for managing product locations within customer fulfillment facilities. Collaborated closely with the product team to reduce scope by 65%, from 15 user stories to 5 core MVP features, while maintaining customer value. Led a team of 10 developers to deliver on an aggressive 5-month timeline. Designed DynamoDB single-table schema with adjacency-matrix pattern for complex location hierarchies.</p></li></ul><p><strong>EDI ML Auto Association</strong></p><ul><li><p>Designed and deployed a backend REST API integrating a machine learning model for automated mapping of customer EDI messages using NLP. Led 6 developers to ship a production ML inference system using AWS SageMaker, launching at re:Invent within a 2-month timeline.</p></li></ul>",
          "roles": []
        },
