          "description": "<p><strong>Hardware Provisioning System</strong></p><ul><li><p>Architected and led implementation of a global hardware provisioning system as single-threaded owner and technical lead. Designed RESTful API with 30+ endpoints and DynamoDB single-table schema to scale to millions of devices across hundreds of sites. Led a team of 5 engineers to deliver 20,000 lines of Python code with Step Functions for async provisioning workflows. System has served 6+ million API requests annually at 99.6%+ availability across all production regions.</p></li></ul>",
          "roles": []
