          "website": { "url": "", "label": "" },
          "description": "<p><strong>Document Security Audit Service</strong></p><ul><li><p>Designed and developed an automated security audit service scanning tens of thousands of user accounts and millions of documents daily for security vulnerabilities. Reduced document bloat by 12TB, saving $1MM+ annually in storage costs. Operated for 6 years with a single incident before successfully deprecating.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Firewall Centralized Log Monitoring</strong></p><ul><li><p>Designed and developed a centralized log monitoring service analyzing log messages from thousands of firewalls globally in near real-time. Detected and alarmed on hundreds of security events including malformed rules and configuration errors.</p></li></ul>",
